name: Girls series #3
description: “Nothing beats the sea at all, what do you keep inside myself at times I fall to my knees before him by two - I start to believe into its bottomlessness and infinity and dissolve in it on the count of three. I can't swim - I don't care, because to these waves I, crucified, sick, I will not prefer freedom because what do I keep and what will I have without your waters, your surf I am forever buried at sea and I blindly believe that apart from this there is no more beauty "
